OBUIAPP_PROCESS.NAME: Kill Process
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.DESCRIPTION: Kill background process if the process implements a kill method.
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.HELP: Kill background process if the process implements a kill method.

OBUIAPP_PROCESS.NAME: Reserved Good Movement Pick and Edit
Validate Costing Rule
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.HELP: Validate and initialize the Costing Rule. It automatically creates and process the Close and Opening Physical inventories to overwrite an existing Costing Rule. If the instance is using the legacy engine costs it is mandatory to run the Cost Migration Process in advance with System Administrator role.

OBUIAPP_PROCESS.NAME: RM Shipment Pick and Edit Lines
Fix Backdated Transactions
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.HELP: Process that recalculates costs of backdated transactions until the given date. Run process from Costing Rules window.

OBUIAPP_PROCESS.NAME: RM Receipt Pick and Edit Lines
Manage Stock Reservation Pick and Edit
Inventory Amount Update
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.DESCRIPTION: Generates 2 closing/opening inventories and generates a cost adjustment document
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.HELP: Generates 2 closing/opening inventories. Closing inventory cost is the inventory amount on that moment. The costing background should be disabled during this process to avoid being it calculated as usual. Opening inventory cost is the desired amount (average). Generates a Cost Adjustment Document so the cost is adjusted to the reference date in case this is a different date than the current one. Sets all transactions prior to the reference date as permanently adjusted.

OBUIAPP_PROCESS.NAME: Grant Portal Access
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.DESCRIPTION: Grants to this user access to portal
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.HELP: Grants to this user access to one of the available portal roles and resets the password for this user.

OBUIAPP_PROCESS.NAME: RFC/RTV HQL Pick and Edit Lines
Set New Currency
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.DESCRIPTION: Sets new currency for the customer
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.HELP: Sets new currency for the customer. If the amount is specified, the new customer balance will be set to this amount. If the exchange rate is specified, the new customer balance will be calculated with the specified exchange rate. If the amount and exchange rates are not specified, default conversion rate will be applied for the new customer balance.

OBUIAPP_PROCESS.NAME: Manual Cost Adjustment
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.DESCRIPTION: Manual Cost Adjustment process: Generates a cost adjustment document. and adds a line for the given transaction.
OBUIAPP_PROCESS.HELP: Manual Cost Adjustment process: Generates a cost adjustment document. and adds a line for the given transaction.
